# Model Card Template (Markdown)
# Based on Mitchell et al. 2019 — Google Research

MODEL_CARD_TEMPLATE = """# Model Card: {model_name}

## Model Details
- **Developer:** {developer}
- **Model Date:** {date}
- **Model Version:** {version}
- **Model Type:** {model_type} (e.g., Transformer, XGBoost, ResNet)
- **Architecture:** {architecture_description}
- **Training Time:** {training_time}
- **Training Hardware:** {hardware}

## Intended Use
- **Primary Intended Uses:** {primary_uses}
- **Primary Intended Users:** {primary_users}
- **Out-of-Scope Uses:** {out_of_scope}

## Factors
- **Relevant Factors:** {factors} (e.g., race, gender, age, language)
- **Evaluation Factors:** {eval_factors} (which factors selected for evaluation)

## Metrics
- **Model Performance Measures:** {metrics}
- **Overall Metrics:**
  - Accuracy: {accuracy}%
  - Precision: {precision}%
  - Recall: {recall}%
  - F1: {f1}%
- **Sliced Metrics (by relevant factor):**
  | Group | Accuracy | Precision | Recall | F1 |
  |-------|----------|-----------|--------|-----|
  | {group1} | {acc1}% | {prec1}% | {rec1}% | {f11}% |
  | {group2} | {acc2}% | {prec2}% | {rec2}% | {f12}% |
- **Fairness Metrics:**
  - Demographic Parity Ratio: {dp_ratio}
  - Equal Opportunity Difference: {eo_diff}

## Evaluation Data
- **Datasets:** {eval_datasets}
- **Preprocessing:** {preprocessing}
- **Labeling:** {labeling_process}
- **Motivation:** {data_motivation}

## Training Data
- **Datasets:** {train_datasets}
- **Preprocessing:** {train_preprocessing}
- **Size:** {train_size} examples
- **Distribution:** {train_distribution}

## Ethical Considerations
- {ethical_considerations}

## Caveats & Recommendations
- {caveats}

---
*Model Card generated on {generation_date}*"""

# Usage: fill template with model-specific values
# print(MODEL_CARD_TEMPLATE.format(model_name='CreditScorer v2', ...))
